Adenike Temidayo Oladiji (amụrụ na 27 Eprel 1968) bụ onye agụmakwụkwọ Naijiria na nwanyị mbụ osote onye isi nke mahadum nka-na-úzú nke gọọmenti etiti di na AkureKọmitii na-achịkwa ụlọ ọrụ ahụ kwadoro nhọpụta ya na nzukọ pụrụ iche nke ha nwere na 13 Mee 2022
Ọ nọchiri prọfesọ Joseph Fuwape, onye oge ya gwụrụ na Mọnde 23 Mee 2022
Tupu nhọpụta ya, ọ nwere ọkwa dị iche iche ma rụọ ọrụ na Kọmitii Mahadum nke Ilorin dị ka Onye isi oche na Onye otu.

Ọ rụkwara ọrụ n'okpuru ikike dị iche iche na Mahadum Ilorin gụnyere Onye isi ngalaba, Sub Dean of Faculty, Osote onye nduzi nke Center for International Education,onye nduzi nke Center for Research and Development and In-House Training, ma onye nduzi Central Research Laboratory

Ọ rụkwara ọrụ dị ka onye-isi ulo akwukwo nke Basic Medical Sciences (Kwara State University), Onye-isiLife ụlọ akwụkwọ nke Sciences, na onye otu ọchịchị Kansụl nke ulo akwụkwọ nke gọọmenti etiti, Nasarawa na Crown Hill University, Eiyenkorin, Ilorin.
